<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bölüm 3: Mükemmel Sayılar</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root { --theme-color: #ffd700; --dark-bg: #0a0a05; --card-bg: #1a1a00; }
        body { background-color: var(--dark-bg); color: #fff; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background-image: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1), transparent 50%); }
        .neon-text { font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; color: var(--theme-color); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--theme-color), 0 0 20px var(--theme-color); }
        .content-box { background: var(--card-bg); border-left: 4px solid var(--theme-color); padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 15px 15px 0; box-shadow: 10px 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .content-box::after { content: '\f3a5'; font-family: "Font Awesome 6 Free"; font-weight: 900; position: absolute; right: -20px; bottom: -30px; font-size: 150px; color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.05); z-index: 0; }
        .example-number { display: inline-block; font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 10px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 1px solid var(--theme-color); border-radius: 10px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .example-number:hover { background: var(--theme-color); color: #000; box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--theme-color); }
        .btn-nav { border: 1px solid var(--theme-color); color: var(--theme-color); background: transparent; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-nav:hover { background: var(--theme-color); color: #000; box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--theme-color); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-down">
            <a href="armstrong.html" class="btn-nav"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i> Geri: Armstrong</a>
            <span class="text-secondary font-monospace">SEVİYE 3 / 5</span>
            <a href="fibonacci.html" class="btn-nav">Sıradaki: Fibonacci <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></a>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-5 text-center mb-4" data-aos="fade-right">
                <i class="fas fa-gem" style="font-size: 10rem; color: var(--theme-color); text-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--theme-color);"></i>
                <h1 class="neon-text mt-4 display-4">MÜKEMMEL</h1>
                <p class="text-muted mt-2">Matematiğin Kusursuz Mücevherleri</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7" data-aos="fade-left">
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h3 class="neon-text fs-4 mb-3">Tam Bir Denge Hikayesi</h3>
                    <p style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">Kendisi hariç pozitif tam bölenlerinin toplamı kendisine eşit olan sayılara denir. Bu sayılar o kadar nadirdir ki, antik çağlardan beri "mükemmelliğin" simgesi olmuşlardır.</p>
                    <h4 class="mt-4 mb-3 text-light">Kusursuz Örnek: 6</h4>
                    <p class="text-secondary">6'nın bölenleri: 1, 2, 3 <br> Toplam: 1 + 2 + 3 = 6!</p>
                    <div class="mt-3">
                        <div class="example-number">6</div>
                        <div class="example-number">28</div>
                        <div class="example-number">496</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>AOS.init();</script>
</body>
</html>
